hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db5274c228f59dbf569fcb47b69780e1c97ec4a5","tid":504561,"uid":67598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T15:55:24.000Z","msg":"好犀利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 巴打以後寫多啲"},{"pid":"2ea0f17836baad498946ff6f2800c812fdac759f","tid":504561,"uid":34427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T16:10:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>就咁睇樓主都比呢種愛情觀所影響<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 到處留情</blockquote><br />\n我都想有胡蘭成既本錢同才學去到處留情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，所以我先用果頭尾果句黎開頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打係讀開文學定點?"},{"pid":"4f741c96eb4b9ed9dbde88a5fdc846d08136a9fb","tid":504561,"uid":80046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T16:20:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好犀利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 巴打以後寫多啲</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a82acd3bffc6a17856ad76afab9b5882bfc4c8e","tid":504561,"uid":152123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T16:21:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>就咁睇樓主都比呢種愛情觀所影響<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 到處留情</blockquote><br />\n我都想有胡蘭成既本錢同才學去到處留情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，所以我先用果頭尾果句黎開頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7664f65bb66d97c87d30f0f50899c91b596d07bd","tid":504561,"uid":80046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T16:22:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>就咁睇樓主都比呢種愛情觀所影響<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 到處留情</blockquote><br />\n我都想有胡蘭成既本錢同才學去到處留情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，所以我先用果頭尾果句黎開頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打係讀開文學定點?</blockquote><br />\n唔係啦，我讀business <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 平時寫開叫春文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 只係本身鐘意歷史同文學既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ff99351c6b03f7bd17517cc199450a282ad2703","tid":504561,"uid":80046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T16:24:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>就咁睇樓主都比呢種愛情觀所影響<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 到處留情</blockquote><br />\n我都想有胡蘭成既本錢同才學去到處留情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，所以我先用果頭尾果句黎開頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n歷史話比人知既係冷冰冰既事實（人性面），但文字寫出黎既係有感情既事實（都係講緊人性面），各有千秋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eae745fe0b8059911d82b679a08863d2a4e5ce94","tid":504561,"uid":73406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T16:30:39.000Z","msg":"樓主攞景定贈興，幅圖應該係錢鍾書嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n錢鍾書睇唔起張愛玲架嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a07e9b4cc9292e6b3e3cda62646d3f0a816a13b","tid":504561,"uid":152123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T16:33:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主攞景定贈興，幅圖應該係錢鍾書嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n錢鍾書睇唔起張愛玲架嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巧合地我好鍾意錢鍾書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8ac7950ab9819380511c63d8b424c4a2bf62791","tid":504561,"uid":80046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T16:36:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主攞景定贈興，幅圖應該係錢鍾書嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n錢鍾書睇唔起張愛玲架嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔知啦，頭尾果句都有關聯下既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fddff07e791e7ee4bf0c3ab83f2f2fb5a8d42e82","tid":504561,"uid":80046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T16:39:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主攞景定贈興，幅圖應該係錢鍾書嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n錢鍾書睇唔起張愛玲架嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cb25e08fea36d9e975eab1c5353b1cdfd43ab02","tid":504561,"uid":120814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T16:39:13.000Z","msg":"無誇張, 睇完胡蘭成, 可以以後都唔睇中文書了"},{"pid":"8bc9dc7529301d5a02050f92d81d79c1386e8836","tid":504561,"uid":152123,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T16:39:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>樓主攞景定贈興，幅圖應該係錢鍾書嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n錢鍾書睇唔起張愛玲架嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巧合地我好鍾意錢鍾書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌我啱啱google完錢鍾書點樣話張愛玲<br />\n我同佢睇法居然係完全一致<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我自從初中開始睇張愛玲嘅書 愈睇愈唔對路"},{"pid":"dfb96daaa1efa5273f6409017d04f565c4fa1ec9","tid":504561,"uid":80046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T16:40:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>樓主攞景定贈興，幅圖應該係錢鍾書嚟<img src=\"/ass