504561,"uid":84646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T17:54:45.000Z","msg":"竟然冇張愛玲嘅紅玫瑰白玫瑰<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6453c99e05724aef9ed233e4440cf8d88f523e85","tid":504561,"uid":84646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T17:55:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>竟然冇張愛玲嘅紅玫瑰白玫瑰<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n也許每一個男子全都有過這樣的兩個女人，至少兩個。娶了紅玫瑰，久而久之，紅的變了牆上的一抹蚊子血，白的還是『床前明月光』；娶了白玫瑰，白的便是衣服上沾的一粒飯黏子，紅的卻是心口上一顆硃砂痣。"},{"pid":"3ef13b90f701ffb95aa9413fbbe43d925d719263","tid":504561,"uid":80046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T18:05:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>竟然冇張愛玲嘅紅玫瑰白玫瑰<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 明明有寫"}]}